                    <div class="row mission-statement aboutus-quote">
                        <div class="quote-mark"><span>"</span></div>
                        <div class="quote-text">
                            eSports Initiative is a collegiate organization that unites recreational and competitive video game players with members of the digital media industry in order to celebrate a passion for gaming, build a stronger sense of community, raise funds for charity, and collectively volunteer in the Greater Columbus Area. Through the hosting of charitable video game events and tournaments, eSports Initiative is able to have direct influence on the growth and improvement of the Midwest eSports scene and local Columbus community.
                        </div>
